                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-slide-right">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Unique Identity</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">
              VeChain ID <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">assignment</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">
              When a device arrives at the warehouse, it's registered on the VeChainThor blockchain and assigned a unique, immutable identifier. This ID follows the device throughout its entire lifecycle.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Automatic Registration</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Devices are registered on receipt scan. No manual blockchain interaction required.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
