                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Cross-Platform Support</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Works with Windows, macOS, iOS, Android, and any device with a serial number.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Lifecycle Events -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="animate-slide-left">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Event Recording</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">
              Every event <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">recorded</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">
              Significant device lifecycle events are automatically recorded to the blockchain. Each record includes timestamp, event type, location, and operator information.
