            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">
              Tamper-proof <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">audit trails</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">
              Generate verifiable audit reports for compliance requirements. Prove complete chain-of-custody for any device at any time with cryptographic certainty.
